<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CareCloud</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .navbar-brand {
            color: #FF69B4 !important;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .btn-login {
            background-color: #FF69B4;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 5px 15px;
        }

        .hero {
            background-color: #F0F8FF;
            padding: 50px 0;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            color: #FF69B4;
        }

        .hero p {
            color: #333;
        }

        .btn-get-started {
            background-color: #4169E1;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
        }

        .section-heading {
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .why-us-section {
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .first-column-content {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            height: 100%;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .first-column-content p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .medcare-logo {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .medcare-logo img {
            width: 220px;
        }

        /* Decreased margin-top for Stats logo to be closer to second-column-text */
        .stats-logo {
            align-self: flex-start;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .stats-logo img {
            width: 215px;
        }

        .second-column-text {
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .second-column-content {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .user-reviews-section {
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        /* Styling for user reviews cards */
        .card {
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            /* Added box-shadow */
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        .card img {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 50%;
            /* Ensuring rounded images */
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            /* Added shadow to user images */
        }

        .card h5 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #FF69B4;
        }

        .card p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #333;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-white">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">CareCloud</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav"
                aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse justify-content-end" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav">
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#">Home</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#">About</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#">Contact</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#">Sign Up</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="btn btn-login" href="#">Login</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h2 class="mb-3">Welcome to CareCloud</h2>
                    <h1 class="mb-3">Your Health, Always Within Reach</h1>
                    <p class="mb-4">At CareCloud, we provide a secure and convenient platform for storing and managing
                        your medical records. Access your important health information anytime, anywhere, all in one
                        place.</p>
                    <button class="btn btn-get-started">Get Started</button>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <img src="/assets/landing/doctor.svg" alt="Medical records illustration" class="img-fluid">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="container why-us-section">
        <div class="section-heading">
            <h2>Why Us?</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <!-- First Column -->
            <div class="col-md-6 d-flex">
                <div class="first-column-content">
                    <p>We prioritize your privacy. CareCloud uses advanced encryption to ensure your medical data is
                        safe and protected from unauthorized access. Your health records are stored securely in the
                        cloud, so you never have to worry about misplacing important documents.</p>

                    <!-- Stats Logo (left side, closer to second-column) -->
                    <div class="stats-logo">
                        <img src="/assets/landing/stats.svg" alt="Medical Security Illustration"
                            style="margin-left: 101px;">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Second Column -->
            <div class="col-md-6 d-flex align-items-center">
                <div class="second-column-content">
                    <!-- Medcare Logo above text -->
                    <div class="medcare-logo">
                        <img src="/assets/landing/medcare.svg" alt="Medcare Logo" style="margin-bottom: 19px;">
                    </div>

                    <!-- Text below the logo -->
                    <div class="second-column-text">
                        <p>Need to send your medical records to a healthcare provider or family member? CareCloud makes
                            sharing simple and secure. You can instantly send the information they need with just a few
                            clicks, giving you control over who sees your data.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- User Reviews Section -->
    <div class="container user-reviews-section">
        <div class="section-heading">
            <h2>User Reviews</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <!-- Review Card 1 -->
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="/assets/review/user1.jpg" alt="User 1">
                    <h5>John Doe</h5>
                    <p>"CareCloud has made it incredibly easy to manage my medical records. I can access them anytime,
                        anywhere!"</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Review Card 2 -->
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="/assets/review/user2.jpg" alt="User 2">
                    <h5>Jane Smith</h5>
                    <p>"I love how simple and secure CareCloud is. Sharing my medical data with my doctor was a
                        breeze."</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Review Card 3 -->
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="/assets/review/user3.jpg" alt="User 3">
                    <h5>Michael Johnson</h5>
                    <p>"The encryption features give me peace of mind knowing that my health data is safe and
                        protected."</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>